scovered,and,the,Knights,discovered,the,existence,they,were,not,prepared,for,”,	“In,the,new,lands,known,as,Velious,their,early,scouts,discovered,the,fate,of,the,Dragon,Horde,It,would,appear,that,the,Dragons,had,retreated,to,and,began,building,anew,in,the,lands,of,Velious,The,Knights,worked,diligently,to,infiltrate,and,eradicate,the,Dragon,menace,Many,fell,in,the,line,of,Duty,not,only,to,the,Iksar,Empire,but,also,to,the,whole,of,Norrath,”,	“Here,is,where,history,fails,us,I,am,afraid,The,records,from,this,point,are,not,clear,as,to,what,happened,Because,the,Knights,did,not,fall,under,the,Rule,of,Cabilis,the,ancestors,of,former,members,and,their,respective,guildhalls,from,stories,and,legends,tell,the,only,records,we,have,of,them,”,	“I,understand,Vorrin,Please,tell,me,what,you,know,This,is,all,truly,fascinating,and,if,I,learn,nothing,more,this,season,this,would,be,worth,a,thousand,seasons,of,exploring,”,	Vorrin,chuckled,a,moment,then,continued,“If,you,were,to,ask,anyone,who,the,‘leader’,of,the,Knights,of,the,Green,Mist,was,many,might,tell,you,the,Dark,Mage,Zarkorsis,Kunzar,due,to,his,tribe’s,history,Others,who,interacted,more,closely,with,the,Knights,might,tell,you,Xorrin,were,their,‘leader’,although,it,is,an,established,fact,that,the,Council,of,Four,held,equal,power,within,the,Order,According,to,Prime,Hierophant,Vek,in,the,Temple,of,Terror,Heyokah,Xorrin,Aarikis,was,a,strong,spiritual,leader,amongst,the,Knights,and,often,played,the,key,role,in,determining,what,direction,the,Knights,would,move,in,next,No,Council,Member,dare,issue,a,vital,order,to,his,Faction,without,first,consulting,with,the,great,Mystic,For,this,reason,Xorrin,is,the,one,we,think,of,when,someone,mentions,the,‘Leader,of,the,Knights’,“,	“Right,you,already,explained,that,”,I,said,with,a,confused,look,upon,my,face,	“Yes,But,this,is,where,it,is,important,You,do,not,see,many,Knights,in,your,travels,do,you,”,Vorrin,asked,of,me,	“No,none,at,all,actually,What,happened,to,them,”,I,inquired,	“Well,the,way,I,understand,it,is,that,Xorrin,had,made,a,gruesome,discovery,hidden,deep,within,a,cave,”,	“A,Cave,What,sort,of,discovery,was,this,”,	“Yes,a,cave,Buried,deep,within,a,mountain,he,found,some,sort,of,an,alter,”,	“But,I,don’t,understand,what,that,has,to,do,with,Xorrin,or,the,Knights,”,	“True,to,his,Cause,to,eradicate,the,Draconian,menace,from,the,face,of,Norrath,Xorrin,set,about,to,meditate,on,this,discovery,It,is,said,that,the,resulting,visions,he,saw,frightened,him,so,much,that,he,could,not,bare,to,relive,them,by,telling,others,Shrouded,in,secrecy,he,selected,a,handful,of,the,most,elite,of,the,Knights,for,a,special,mission,They,departed,for,Permafrost,where,they,would,train,for,this,special,mission,for,3,months,time,Grand,Master,Jeet,Lee,reported,seeing,Xorrin,and,his,5,handpicked,companions,from,time,to,time,as,they,made,infrequent,runs,to,Qeynos,for,supplies,It,would,appear,that,Xorrin,was,somehow,able,to,find,friends,within,the,ruling,class,of,Qeynos,who,permitted,him,to,enter,the,Human,city,to,re-supply,Never,however,would,he,discuss,the,mission,with,Jeet,The,rest,of,the,Council,Members,grew,weary,of,this,mission,but,trusted,too,deeply,in,Xorrin’s,powers,and,foresight,to,question,his,motives,”,	“During,a,routine,scouting,mission,Zarkorsis,and,Sashara,reported,having,spotted,Xorrin,and,his,team,returning,to,the,ice,lands,of,Velious,They,gathered,what,they,could,carry,from,their,camp,and,followed,him,to,a,cave,Xorrin’s,group,prepared,themselves,with,the,most,powerful,of,magical,incantations,that,Zarkorsis,had,ever,seen,Finally,they,cast,themselves,into,invisibility,which,Zarkorsis,and,Sashara,were,both,able,to,see,through,thanks,to,their,own,incantations,and,entered,the,cave,”,	“Hiding,themselves,in,a,similar,fashion,the,two,Council,Members,followed,Xorrin’s,group,from,a,safe,distance,curious,to,see,what,he,had,held,in,secrecy,for,so,long,The,caves,were,lined,with,life-sized,statues,of,dragons,of,all,breed,and,lineage,An,alter,stood,at,the,end…”,	“You,see,the,alter,was,in,all,actuality,a,key,”,	“What,sort,of,key,”,I,asked,finding,myself,leaning,ever,closer,to,Vorrin,as,not,to,miss,any,detail,	“The,alter,was,the,key,to,a,great,city,A,city,far,more,glorious,than,that,of,even,the,Dwarves,of,Thurgadin,A,city,far,larger,and,more,towering,than,Kael,itself,A,city,of,Dragon-kind,”,	I,could,not,help,but,to,gasp,aloud,in,awe,at,the,sheer,magnitude,of,what,Xorrin,had,discovered,To,imagine,a,city,of,Dragons,was,just,more,than,I,could,handle,at,the,moment,The,size,of,the,thing,would,fill,a,score,of,Freeports,Hundreds…nay…thousands,of,dragons,living,and,working,together,as,an,organized,society,If,such,a,thing,were,indeed,true,the,implications,on,all,of,Norrath,would,be,devastating,No,land,no,society,could,withstand,an,assault,of,such,magnitude,if,they,were,to,attack,	“Something,went,terribly,wrong,though,Sashara’s,invisibility,spell,wore,off,not,far,into,the,city,The,draconian,guards,lining,the,walls,immediately,took,note,of,her,presence,Zarkorsis,was,forced,to,break,his,veil,also,and,both,began,to,Gate,out,of,the,area,in,the,brief,confusion,of,the,surprise,”,	“That,wasn’t,the,worst,of,it,though,Before,they,escaped,Sashara,noticed,that,Xorrin’s,group,had,also,lost,their,invisibility,Perhaps,some,unexpected,Dragon,enchantment,protected,the,area,from,invisible,intruders,To,this,day,no,one,knows,exactly,what,the,cause,was,”,	“The,last,thing,Sashara,reported,to,the,Knights,was,that,she,saw,Xorrin,valiantly,healing,and,aiding,his,companions,in,an,overwhelming,battle,He,looked,her,in,the,eye,she,said,and,told,her,to,never,return,or,speak,of,this,place,again,but,to,prepare,the,Knights,for,what,he,hoped,would,never,happen,Sashara,gated,out,just,behind,Zarkorsis,and,none,of,the,others,were,ever,seen,again,”,	I,could,not,control,the,feelings,welling,up,inside,me,at,this,tragic,tale,of,bravery,not,only,for,the,Iksar,but,for,all,of,Norrath,We,were,so,wrong,the,Humans,the,Elves,the,Gnomes,and,Halflings,and,the,Dwarves,for,our,decades,of,mistreatment,of,the,Iksar,Had,we,but,taken,the,time,to,learn,of,their,past,their,spirit,we,would,better,understand,their,ways,Aye,the,God,they,worship,is,Cazic-Thule,but,as,we,have,seen,in,others,it,is,not,the,God,that,shapes,its,people,it,is,the,actions,of,their,heroes,and,leaders,	“What,happened,to,the,Knights,after,that,Why,are,they,not,still,around,”,I,just,had,to,know,now,	“Hehe…you,truly,do,enjoy,our,history,don’t,you,Isak,Very,well,I,shall,tell,you,all,you,wish,to,know,”,	“The,Knights,trained,hard,for,many,months,after,Xorrin’s,disappearance,It,did,not,take,long,however,for,the,lower-ranking,Knights,to,figure,out,that,their,Leader,was,missing,Try,as,they,might,the,Council,simply,could,not,hold,them,together,much,longer,The,loss,of,Xorrin,was,much,too,significant,a,loss,for,the,Knights,and,delivered,a,crippling,blow,to,their,morale,One,from,which,it,seemed,they,would,never,recover,”,	“Realizing,that,their,efforts,to,hold,the,Knights,together,were,slowly,slipping,from,their,grasp,the,Council,formulated,a,new,plan,Jeet,and,Sashara,would,form,new,alliances,and,reunite,the,lost,Knights,under,the,banner,of,‘Tempest,of,Fate’,A,new,storm,was,brewing,and,the,Tempest,of,Fate,would,be,the,salvation,of,all,that,the,Knights,stood,for,”,	“But…what,happened,to,them,”,I,asked,not,having,seen,any,of,their,members,for,many,seasons,	“Unprepared,for,the,task,at,hand,some,of,the,leadership,of,the,Tempest,of,Fate,fell,to…human…ways,Sorry,to,have,to,put,it,that,way,but…”,	“No,apology,needed,friend,I,understand,exactly,what,you,mean,”,I,interrupted,	Vorrin,continued,“It,did,not,take,long,for,the,Tempest,of,Fate,to,collapse,No,one,outside,the,Council,of,Fate,knows,truly,what,happened,A,few,Knights,remained,loyal,however,and,still,roam,the,lands,in,secrecy,Today,they,serve,more,as,information,gatherers,and,scouts,keeping,tabs,on,the,Dragon,horde,and,tipping,off,the,larger,organizations,better,equipped,to,handle,such,threats,”,	“Ahh,I,see,Then,I,assume,that,amulet,you,wear,is,”,	“Very,good,Ranger,Your,eyes,are,well,trained,indeed,”,	“And,you,last,name…are,you,”,I,asked,	“Am,I,I,am,an,Aarikis,yes,One,of,the,if,not,the,last,of,my,tribe,I,am,not,however,the,leader,of,the,Knights,We,have,no,leader,but,rather,operate,under,a,secret,code,of,honor,to,one,another,and,to,our,Cause,I’m,afraid,that,we,do,not,even,know,how,many,of,us,are,left,Rarely,do,we,cross,paths,except,when,welcoming,new,Knights,into,the,Order,or,our,tasks,bring,us,otherwise,together,”,	“Have,you,ever,considered,re-forming,the,Knights,Gathering,all,your,resources,together,and,making,an,assault,upon,the,Dragon,city,”,	“For,one,we,do,not,even,know,where,it,is,Those,who,do,know,Zarkorsis,and,Sashara,have,gone,their,own,ways,and,refuse,still,to,tell,all,that,they,saw,All,is,not,lost,though,Rest,assured,that,the,Knights,are,still,here,and,we,continue,to,make,a,significant,impact,in,the,service,of,Norrath,”,	“Indeed,”,That,was,all,I,could,say,and,we,just,sat,there,for,what,seemed,to,be,hours,staring,off,into,the,stars,The,fire,crackled,softly,in,the,background,as,a,zephyr,cooled,our,bodies,and,minds,	I,presented,Vorrin,with,the,book,I,had,brought,for,him,and,we,spent,the,next,couple,hours,discussing,the,many,illustrations,and,locations,of,Antonica,while,we,ate,a,freshly,caught,Deepwater,Barracuda,	Some,time,passed,until,we,were,suddenly,interrupted,by,a,group,of,fortune,seekers,running,through,our,camp,“What,have,you,Can’t,you,see,we’ve,set,a,camp,here,”,	“Hail,sire,My,apologies,”,replied,a,robed,Gnome,“We’ve,just,heard,word,of,a,new,portal,being,discovered,Takes,ye,to,the,moon,they,say,Plenty,of,cheese,we’re,off,to,gather,Moon,cheese,should,bring,a,nice,profit,don’t,ya,agree,”,	“What’s,this,nonsense,you’re,talking,”,I,asked,more,frustrated,at,the,disturbance,than,the,foolishness,	“In,the,name,of,Cazic,it,cannot,be,”,Vorrin,looked,as,if,death,itself,were,upon,him,	“What,is,it,Will,someone,speak,sense,here,”,I,shouted,	Vorrin,was,first,“I,have,seen,these,images…images,of,a,massive,portal,linking,all,others…images,of,a,sky,where,the,sun,and,the,moon,did,not,rise,and,fall,but,Norrath,itself,Images,of…”,He,did,not,complete,his,thought,	“Images,of,what,lizard,”,the,Gnome,impatiently,retorted,	“No,It,cannot,be,”,Vorrin,fell,silent,at,that,“If,you,will,excuse,me,I,must,meditate,and,consult,the,Spirits,of,the,Ancients,”,	The,Gnome’s,companions,were,calling,to,him,to,hurry,less,they,leave,him,behind,Not,wanting,to,miss,out,on,his,share,of,the,cheese,profits,he,ran,off,without,so,much,as,excusing,himself,	“Come,Vorrin,Consult,the,Spirits,later,Let,us,go,and,see,what,is,amuck,”,	We,soon,found,ourselves,standing,at,the,spires,in,Dreadlands,Lying,on,the,ground,in,the,middle,was,an,Iksar,obviously,a,Shaman,Vorrin,immediately,ran,to,his,aid,as,no,others,would,help,him,	Badly,beaten,bloodied,and,near,death,the,Scaled,Mystic,was,able,to,utter,only,these,words,in,Elder,Dragon,as,translated,by,an,on,looking,Wizard,when,he,glanced,up,to,see,Vorrin,at,his,side…,	“They,have,not,perished,They,survive,We,must,hurry,Gather,our,forces,son,There,is,much,work,to,be,done,and,no,time,to,waste,Hurry,I,say,We,must,put,a,stop,to,the,Shissar,before,it,is,too,late,”,	Vorrin,cast,his,Healing,spell,as,the,mysterious,Iksar,fell,unconscious,Help,me,Ranger,I,must,get,him,to,the,Temple,of,Terror,before,it,is,too,late,I,will,help,you,past,the,guards,	As,we,turned,the,old,Shaman,over,to,lift,him,I,noticed,he,wore,an,amulet,similar,to,the,one,Vorrin,wore,Similar,yet,different,for,his,was,larger,and,glowed,with,a,mysterious,light,It,was,almost,as,if,it,were,not,of,this,world,but,of,the,Spirit,World,like,the,Spirit,Companions,the,Mystics,often,travel,with,	Vorrin,took,note,of,it,also,As,we,carried,the,Iksar,away,Iksar,are,quite,heavy,by,the,way,I,heard,Vorrin,say,under,his,breath,in,the,Lizard,tongue,“Do,not,fear,Xorrin,for,I,shall,mend,your,suffering,The,Knights,will,reunite,under,your,call,”,	It,would,appear,as,I’ve,said,many,a,time,this,evening,that,all,is,not,as,it,seems…" />
